Dear Sir,
My name is Franck Hamidou Ali , a retired Investment
Banker. I have a former client who has interest in a joint venture
investment, she has funds available for this purpose. My client is a
Turkish citizen, she belongs to the elite political class. For this
reason, she wants to remain anonymous.

We can discuss further if you are interested in partnering with us.
Expecting your feedback soon

Kind regards,
Franck Hamidou Ali
